### Summary of Changes:
1. **TypeScript Contract Parity**: Updated [packages/contracts/src/index.ts](file:///D:/Work/Codex/Hackathon%20Projects/OpenAI%20Hackathon/.agent-worktrees/incident-m2-frontend/packages/contracts/src/index.ts) to define complete backend fields on the `EvidenceItem` interface (`provider`, `content_hash`, `display_ref`, `redaction_rules`, `captured_at`).
2. **Complete Golden Evidence Rendering**: Modified the incident room's Evidence Panel in [apps/web/app/incidents/\[id\]/page.tsx](file:///D:/Work/Codex/Hackathon%20Projects/OpenAI%20Hackathon/.agent-worktrees/incident-m2-frontend/apps/web/app/incidents/%5Bid%5D/page.tsx) to render a clean, high-density metadata grid showing Captured time, display reference, content SHA-256 hash, provider, and source. Included clear simulated labels (`🤖 SIMULATED`) and redaction state labels (`🔒 REDACTED`), and displayed redaction rules and raw sanitized content on card expansion.
3. **Timeline Chronology & Focus Scroll**: Sorted timeline events in stable chronological ascending order. Added an interactive click handler that expands the cited evidence card, scrolls it smoothly into view, sets keyboard focus, and triggers a temporary glow animation using `.evidence-highlighted` in [apps/web/app/global.css](file:///D:/Work/Codex/Hackathon%20Projects/OpenAI%20Hackathon/.agent-worktrees/incident-m2-frontend/apps/web/app/global.css).
