5. **Visible API Failures**: Tracked and displayed evidence and timeline API fetch errors inside high-visibility warning blocks instead of silently passing.
6. **E2E Playwright Tests**: Added [apps/web/e2e/golden-evidence.spec.ts](file:///D:/Work/Codex/Hackathon%20Projects/OpenAI%20Hackathon/.agent-worktrees/incident-m2-frontend/apps/web/e2e/golden-evidence.spec.ts) asserting the complete demo reset, start progress checklist, evidence bundle matching metrics, chronology, and provenance.
